```mermaid
%%{init: {'theme': 'base'}}%%
graph TB
    subgraph ContextFlow["Context/Checkpoint Flow"]
        START[Start Turn] --> CHK[Create Checkpoint]
        CHK --> STEP[Run Step]
        STEP --> DMAIL{D-Mail?}
        DMAIL -->|Yes| REVERT[Revert to Checkpoint]
        DMAIL -->|No| NEXT{Continue?}
        REVERT --> INJECT[Inject D-Mail Message]
        INJECT --> CHK
        NEXT -->|Yes| CHK
        NEXT -->|No| END[End Turn]
    end
    
    style ContextFlow fill:#e8f5e9
```

