```mermaid
%%{init: {'theme': 'base'}}%%
graph LR
    subgraph CompactionFlow["Compaction Flow"]
        CHECK{Token Count<br/>> Threshold?} -->|Yes| PREP[Prepare Messages]
        CHECK -->|No| SKIP[Skip]
        PREP --> SPLIT[Split: to_compact +<br/>to_preserve]
        SPLIT --> LLM_SUMM[LLM Summarize<br/>to_compact]
        LLM_SUMM --> MERGE[Merge: Summary +<br/>Preserved Messages]
        MERGE --> REPLACE[Replace Context]
    end
    
    style CompactionFlow fill:#fce4ec
```

